You can simply ask Alexa to control your Jaquar products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our “Jaquar Smart” app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our “Jaquar Smart” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search “Jaquar Smart” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable “Jaquar Smart” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Jaquar Smart” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 20%.”
“Alexa, turn on the plug.”
